{"id":"1de26e17-192e-43b9-8598-596abcce0fd8","title":"1498/05/22: The sacrifice of the three Frati was made","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"a67b2dac-cf03-4f32-aee2-f846b9d3b23a","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"22nd May (Wednesday morning). The sacrifice of the three Frati was made. They took them out of the Palagio and brought them on to the ringhiera, where were assembled the \u0022Eight\u0022 and the Collegi, the papal envoy, the General of the Dominicans, and many canons, priests and monks of divers Orders, and the Bishop of the Pagagliotti who was deputed to degrade the three Frati; and here on the ringhiera the said ceremony was to be performed. They were robed in all their vestments, which were taken off one by one, with the appropriate words for the degradation, it being constantly affirmed that Fra Girolamo was a heretic and schismatic, and on this account condemned to be burnt; then their faces and hands were shaved, as is customary in this ceremony.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"7bb41984-9785-4b9b-ae84-37fcca50c642","type":"codex/time-reference","start":0,"end":27,"value":"1691f7af-40e3-48b9-9be0-e9812595b43e","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"64c98e71-f1a5-4df9-ad89-e1282d7e0583","type":"style/superscript","start":2,"end":3,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"e57d744b-048f-441e-92a6-033cdc988182","type":"style/italics","start":57,"end":61,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"7dea953e-9e2e-4901-b82c-c38102596ec5","type":"language","start":57,"end":61,"value":"it","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"e3b1add8-4765-4bb3-b54f-7177fd98daf2","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":57,"end":61,"value":"e579cc17-ad7d-44b1-a270-b85cb7bf90fa","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"bb51d57c-bb76-42a1-99be-998f5856e5a3","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":83,"end":86,"value":"e579cc17-ad7d-44b1-a270-b85cb7bf90fa","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"cfa1048e-2474-47ed-aff2-555363afa190","type":"sty